01C%3BDo%20not%20leave%20Jerusalem%20until%20the%20Father%20sends%20you%20the%20gift%20he%20promised%2C%20as%20I%20told%20you%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22red%22%3EJohn%20baptized%20with%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A5%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ein%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%201%3A5b.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20water%2C%20but%20in%20just%20a%20few%20days%20you%20will%20be%20baptized%20with%20the%20Holy%20Spirit.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Ascension%20of%20Jesus%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20when%20the%20apostles%20were%20with%20Jesus%2C%20they%20kept%20asking%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLord%2C%20has%20the%20time%20come%20for%20you%20to%20free%20Israel%20and%20restore%20our%20kingdom%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20replied%2C%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22red%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20Father%20alone%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20set%20those%20dates%20and%20times%2C%20and%20they%20are%20not%20for%20you%20to%20know.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22red%22%3EBut%20you%20will%20receive%20power%20when%20the%20Holy%20Spirit%20comes%20upon%20you.%20And%20you%20will%20be%20my%20witnesses%2C%20telling%20people%20about%20me%20everywhere%26%23x2014%3Bin%20Jerusalem%2C%20throughout%20Judea%2C%20in%20Samari